{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20171.jpg","chara":[{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-50,"posY":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-1"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]There's a high possibility that it is.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Your wish is related to your mother's@fortune telling abilities."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, manifesting the power of foresight@isn't all that surprising."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":0,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Foresight...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That means the future's yours@to shape how you please...right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Um, actually...@I don't think it's that simple."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-7"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So, I mentioned how I saw a vision@of giving you directions, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's not that I saw the future and@changed it..."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Rather, I saw a future that was@already changed."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Wait, so that means...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The future can't be changed."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Once I see it, that future becomes@an absolute reality."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]My mom's ability to see the future@functioned similarly."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I see..."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So...there's no way to make use@of that power...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh, no. I don't think that's the case."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-17"},{"id":250301,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If I wasn't satisfied with a particular future,@I'd definitely take a different action."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-18"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Which means, the future that I ultimately@observe is always one that I'm satisfied with."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Basically, I always see the@\"best\" solution immediately!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-20"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...Probably."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]\"Probably\"...isn't very convincing."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-50,"posY":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-22"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But if what Mabayu says is true..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-002-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You two may become an unbeatable duo!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
